  "title": "Dental Clinic Assistant",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Highlights</strong></u></p><p>5.5 Days work week</p><p>Hours between 9.30am - 7.30pm shift </p><p>Dental & medical benefits</p><p>Bonus for good performances</p><p><br /></p><p><u><strong>Responsibilities</strong></u></p><ul><li>Managing front desk like answering inquiries, scheduling of appointments and patient’s registration.</li><li>Prepare treatment room and instruments.</li><li>Chair-side assisting of treatment procedures.</li><li>Maintain hygiene and sterile standards of instruments, equipments, and materials</li></ul><p><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></p><ul><li>One weekend Saturday/Sunday (5.5 days work week, 44 hrs/week, 5 days possible)</li><li>Experience preferred but on the job training will be provided for those with no prior experience.</li><li>Interested applicants may email your resume to manager@oxleydental.sg</li></ul>",
